Code:
x=int(input("Enter a month number:"))
if x==1:
    print("January has 31 days")
elif x==2:
    print("This year February had 28 days")
elif x==3:
    print("March has 31 days")
elif x==4:
    print("April has 30 days")
elif x==5:
    print("May has 31 days")
elif x==6:
    print("June has 30 days")
elif x==7:
    print("July has 31 days")
elif x==8:
    print("August has 31 days")
elif x==9:
    print("September has 30 days")
elif x==10:
    print("October has 31 days")
elif x==11:
    print("November has 30 days")
elif x==12:
    print("December has 31 days")
Output:
Enter a month number:11
November has 30 days

5.
Code:
a=int(input("Enter the 1st side of the triangle:"))
b=int(input("Enter the 2nd side of the triangle:"))
c=int(input("Enter the 3rd side of the triangle:"))
r=(a**2)+(b**2)

if r==(c**2):
    print("This is a right angled triangle")
elif a==b==c:
    print("This is an equilateral triangle")
elif a==b or a==c or b==c:
    print("This is an isosceles triangle")
elif a!=b and a!=c and b!=c:
    print("This is a scalene triangle")

Output:
Enter the 1st side of the triangle:3
Enter the 2nd side of the triangle:4
Enter the 3rd side of the triangle:5
This is a right angled triangle

6.
Code(1st way- used greater than):
a=int(input("Enter the 1st number:"))
b=int(input("Enter the 2nd number:"))
c=int(input("Enter the 3rd number:"))

if a>b and a>c:
    print("1st one is the biggest number")
elif b>a and b>c:
    print("2nd one is the biggest number")
else:
    print("3rd one is the biggest number")

Output:
Enter the 1st number:4
Enter the 2nd number:5
Enter the 3rd number:7
3rd one is the biggest number

Code(2nd way- used less than):
a=int(input("Enter the 1st number:"))
b=int(input("Enter the 2nd number:"))
c=int(input("Enter the 3rd number:"))

if a<c and b<c:
    print("3rd one is the biggest number")
elif b<a and c<a:
    print("1st one is the biggest number")
else:
    print("2nd one is the biggest number")

Output:
Enter the 1st number:4
Enter the 2nd number:56
Enter the 3rd number:2
2nd one is the biggest number

Code(3rd way- used nested if):
a=int(input("Enter the 1st number:"))
b=int(input("Enter the 2nd number:"))
c=int(input("Enter the 3rd number:"))

if a>b:
    if a>c:
        print("1st one is the biggest number")
elif b>a:
    if b>c:
        print("2nd one is the biggest number")
    else:
        print("3rd one is the biggest number")

Output:
Enter the 1st number:2
Enter the 2nd number:3
Enter the 3rd number:4
3rd one is the biggest number
